data.description: Welcome home to the beautiful Golden Gate Estates. This stunning practically new property offers a perfect blend of comfort and spaciousness. With 4 bedrooms and 2 full baths this home provides ample space for all your needs. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas perfect for entertaining guests or simply enjoying quality time with your loved ones. The well-appointed kitchen features modern appliances, ample counter space, and a convenient breakfast bar. Step outside onto the expansive 2.81 acre lot. The possibilities are endless, whether you envision a tranquil garden, a sparkling pool, or a relaxing patio area for al fresco dining. This outdoor space is a blank canvas, ready to be transformed into your own personal paradise. Close to shopping and restaurants, this home offers the perfect balance of privacy, space, and convenience.
